### Create a task
POST http://localhost:3000/api/projects/PROJECT_ID/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "title": "Implement user authentication",
  "description": "Create login and registration endpoints",
  "priority": "high",
  "dueDate": "2024-02-15",
  "estimatedHours": 8,
  "assignees": ["USER_ID"],
  "tags": ["backend", "security"]
}

### Get all tasks in project
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects/PROJECT_ID/tasks
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Get tasks with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/projects/PROJECT_ID/tasks?status=in-progress&assignee=USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Create a subtask
POST http://localhost:3000/api/projects/PROJECT_ID/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "parentTaskId": "PARENT_TASK_ID",
  "title": "Create JWT utility",
  "priority": "high",
  "estimatedHours": 2
}

### Update task status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/TASK_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "status": "in-progress"
}

### Add dependency
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/TASK_ID/dependencies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "dependencyTaskId": "OTHER_TASK_ID",
  "type": "blocked-by"
}

### Add comment
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/TASK_ID/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "text": "Started working on this. Should be done by EOD."
}